{"tid":503820,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"圈內大佬套現走人　比特幣夢何時醒？ (15:55)","createTime":"2017-12-19T09:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T10:42:46.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f7e0d586aaa37216dd30cf8865fcde44c97142","tid":503820,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171219/img/20171219155542fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171219%2Fimg%2F20171219155542fi_p1.jpg&h=6dd17e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a015bc4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】比特幣網(<a href=\"http://Bitcoin.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBitcoin.com&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=49f32091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bitcoin.com</a>)聯合創始人兼首席技術官埃米爾奧爾登堡(Emil Oldenburg)已經將所持有的比特幣「套現」，他直稱比特幣是目前風險最高的投資。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，奧爾登堡最近賣掉了所持有的比特幣，換成了比特幣現金。比特幣現金是今年8月從比特幣從分離出來的一種衍生品，最近超過以太幣成為全球第二大加密貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n奧爾登堡指出，比特幣最大的缺陷是交易成本高和交易確認時間長，一旦人們意識到這就是它的運作方式，他們就會開始出售比特幣。<br />\n<br />\n據報，現在比特幣交易的確認時間最長可達12小時，每筆交易費最近達到了26美元。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，比特幣現金才是未來，並指出比特幣現金的交易費低至每筆約0.012美元，而且交易瞬間完成，毋需等待交易確認。<br />\n<br />\n目前比特幣網正在與比特幣劃清界限，甚至停止了圍繞比特幣的開發服務，而專注於比特幣現金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171219/20171219155542fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171219%2F20171219155542fi.html&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=042ebd21\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171219/20171219155542fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"1d84b1abedcaae0b357d204af44393a9f944202e","tid":503820,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"話唔定係bitcoin cash is king<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6850cc5eb0edbe25ace515b3661f21b0b3db97f","tid":503820,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"【Bitcoin狂潮】南韓金融監管機構︰「虛擬貨幣非貨幣」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171219/large/1513673203_a1be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F1513673203_a1be.jpg&h=a3d39cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓金融監督管理局星期二表示，並不看待Bitcoin這種虛擬貨幣以及其他加密貨幣，作為任何形式的貨幣，故此不打算立例監管其相關交易。雖然當局上周公佈對Bitcoin的有關規定，但局長Choe Heung-sik指︰「現時唯一能夠做的就是警告投資者，既然Bitcoin不是任何形式的貨幣，將不會受到監管當局進一步擴大規管範圍。」<br />\n<br />\n局方重申，此舉為免向虛擬貨幣投資者發放錯誤訊息，以為更多新監管條例出台，是為了將虛擬貨幣納入成為正式貨幣鋪路。<br />\n另一邊廂，南韓虛擬貨幣交易所Youbit公佈，交易所再度遭到黑客攻擊，造成相當其總資產17%的損失，不過未有透露具體損失金額。現時已停止交易，交易所將會申請破產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171219/57601672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57601672&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2FppW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ab857dc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F57601672&h=285896f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171219/57601672</a>"},{"pid":"90691d3ba248c871e2802fba91746f866a8d1dc3","tid":503820,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"Tulip bubble<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}